Flow -- ( Major Steps)
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
1. Find out the URLs of the webpages for that particular product
2. Read the webpages.
3. Find out the prices.
4. Compare prices, determine the lowest.
5. Send mail with the lowest, price and URL of that website.
6. Also add in the price that different websites are offering.
